<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>418 - I'm a Teapot | Ella Rises</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --er-pink: #FFD8D1;
            --er-pink-dark: #ff9fc4;
            --er-text: #222222;
        }

        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: var(--er-text);
        }

        /* Wrapper for sticky footer */
        .page-wrap {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* DM Serif Display for headers */
        h1, h2, h3, h4, .navbar-brand {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
        }

        /* Reuse Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background-color: var(--er-pink) !important;
            padding: 0.8rem 0;
            min-height: 55px;
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--er-text);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar-brand img {
            height: 50px;
            width: auto;
        }

        /* Main Content Container */
        .teapot-section {
            flex: 1; 
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
        }

        .teapot-card {
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
        }

        .teapot-title {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
            color: var(--er-text);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .teapot-subtitle {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--er-pink-dark); 
        }

        .teapot-img-container {
            /* Removed background color so the transparent image blends in */
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .teapot-img-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-height: 350px; /* Made slightly larger */
        }

        .teapot-text {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* Footer Reuse */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--er-pink);
            padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: auto;
        }
        
        .footer-logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-logo img { height: 40px; width: auto; }
        .footer-bottom { text-align: center; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-top: 2rem; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-wrap">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-light">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/images/ella_logo.avif" alt="Ella Rises Logo">
                <span>Ella Rises</span>
            </a>
            <div class="ms-auto">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Return Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="teapot-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <div class="teapot-card">
                        <h1 class="teapot-title">418</h1>
                        <h2 class="teapot-subtitle">Short & Stout</h2>
                        
                        <div class="teapot-img-container">
                            <img src="/images/teapot.jpeg" alt="Cute Pink Teapot Illustration">
                        </div>

                        <p class="teapot-text">
                            Oops! You've tried to brew coffee on a teapot.
                            <br>
                            This server is currently <strong>refusing</strong> to brew coffee because it is a teapot.
                        </p>

                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg">
                            Go Back to Home
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="footer-logo">
                        <img src="/images/ella_logo.avif" alt="Ella Rises Logo">
                        <span>Ella Rises</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Empowering the rising generation to brew success, 
                        even when the server is a teapot.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end">
                    <p><strong>Quick Links</strong></p>
                    <p><a href="/" style="color: var(--er-text); text-decoration: none;">Home Page</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2025 Ella Rises. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>